      "description": "A simple and easy-to-use Clash controller management app that supports multiple Clash cores and OpenWrt systems, offering intuitive server management and proxy configuration features.\n\n\nMain Features\n\nServer Management\n\n- Multiple server support: Manage multiple Clash controllers at the same time\n- Server status monitoring: Display server connection status and version information in real time\n- Quick add: Supports both Clash Controller and OpenWrt server types\n- Server configuration editing: Modify server parameters and connection settings\n\n\nProxy Management\n\n- Proxy group management: View and manage all proxy groups\n- Node switching: Quickly switch nodes within a proxy group\n- Latency testing: Test node latency and display results\n- Global mode switching: Supports Global, Rule, and Direct modes\n\n\nNetwork Monitoring\n\n- Real-time speed monitoring: Display upload and download speeds\n- Network status detection: Monitor network connection status\n\n\nConfiguration Management\n\n- Configuration file editing: Edit Clash configuration files online\n- Configuration list management: View and manage multiple configuration files\n- Subscription info display: Show remaining traffic and expiration date of subscriptions\n\n\nUser Experience\n\n- Multi-theme support: Light mode, dark mode, and eye-care mode\n- Multi-language support: Chinese and English interfaces\n- Responsive design: Adapted for different screen sizes\n- Custom settings: Configurable options such as request timeout and status check intervals",
